%20and%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20injured%20in%20a%20stampede%20that%20broke%20out%20on%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%20Saturday%20and%20Sunday%20at%20New%20Delhi%20Railway%20Station%20as%20a%20horde%20of%20passengers%20jostled%20to%20make%20way%20to%20trains%20enroute%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Prayagraj%2C%20where%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20is%20underway.%20Among%20the%20dead%20were%2011%20women%20and%20four%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20vendor%20at%20the%20station%20told%20ANI%20that%20around%209%20pm%2C%20crowds%20on%20the%20overbridge%20between%20platforms%2014%20and%2015%20were%20so%20large%20that%20even%20the%20police%20were%20rendered%20helpless.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20platform%20change.%20This%20incident%20happened%20despite%20special%20trains%20running%20every%2030%20minutes%20all%20through%20the%20night.%20In%20my%2026%20years%20at%20this%20station%2C%20I%20have%20never%20seen%20such%20a%20crowd%2C%20not%20even%20on%20Chhath%20Puja.%20So%20much%20force%20was%20deployed%2C%20including%20the%20NDRF%2C%20but%20people%20were%20not%20paying%20heed%20to%20their%20instructions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Stampede%20at%20New%20Delhi%20railway%20station%20%7C%20An%20eyewitness%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20crowd%20was%20beyond%20the%20limit%2C%20people%20were%20gathered%20at%20the%20(foot%20over)%20bridge...%20Such%20a%20huge%20crowd%20wasn't%20expected.%20I%20have%20never%20seen%20such%20a%20massive%20crowd%20at%20the%20railway%20station%2C%20even%20during%20the%20festivals.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FHt6xJjNPpc%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FHt6xJjNPpc%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%