that%20something%20was%20amiss%20since%205%20pm%20on%20Saturday%20when%20it%20took%20him%20one%20hour%20to%20exit%20New%20Delhi%20Metro%20station%2C%20which%20usually%20takes%20just%20two%20minutes.%20He%20was%20also%20present%20when%20the%20stampede%20on%20Mauni%20Amawasya%20occurred%20in%20Prayagraj%2C%20killing%2030%20people%2C%20and%20saw%20a%20pattern%20in%20the%20way%20the%20crowds%20swelled%20in%20no%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20climbed%20down%20to%20Platforms%2013%20and%2014%20and%20shouted%20and%20urged%20passengers%20to%20wait%20for%202-3%20days%20and%20then%20travel%20to%20Prayagraj%20if%20they%20can't%20find%20a%20place%20today.%20What%20can%20the%20authorities%20do%20to%20manage%20a%20crowd%20of%2010%2C000%20people%20that%20is%20not%20listening%20to%20their%20instructions.%20People%20continued%20to%20rush%20to%20whichever%20platform%20there%20was%20an%20announcement%20for%20regarding%20a%20train%20leaving%20for%20Prayagraj.%20I%20helped%20pick%20up%203-4%20people%20and%20put%20them%20in%20Delhi%20Police%20cars%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20passenger%20Pramod%20Chaurasia%20told%20PTI%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20sleeper-class%20ticket%20for%20Purushottam%20Express%20but%20even%20those%20with%20confirmed%20tickets%20could%20not%20board%20the%20train.%20One%20of%20my%20friends%20and%20a%20female%20passenger%20got%20stuck%20in%20the%20crowd.%20There%20was%20too%20much%20pushing%20and%20jostling.%20We%20managed%20to%20stay%20safe%20by%20waiting%20outside%20with%20our%20children.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20official%20statement%2C%20the%20deputy%20commissioner%20of%20police%20(railway)%20said%20platform%20number%2014%20was%20already%20very%20crowded%20when%20the%20Prayagraj%20Express%20train%20was%20waiting%20there%20for%20its%20departure.%20The%20officer%20said%20Swatantra%20Senani%20Express%20and%20Bhubaneshwar%20Rajdhani%20Express%20were%20delayed%20and%20the%20passengers%20of%20these%20trains%20were%20also%20pr