719911%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estampede%20occurred%20at%20New%20Delhi%20Railway%20Station%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20loss%20of%2018%20lives%20on%20Saturday%20night.%20The%20incident%20occurred%20around%2010%20pm%20when%20thousands%20of%20devotees%20were%20heading%20to%20Prayagraj%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F20-000-reunited-with-families-through-digital-lost-and-found-at-maha-kumbh-7718154%5C%22%3EMaha%20Kumbh%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%20festival%2C%20causing%20severe%20overcrowding%20at%20the%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20eyewitness%2C%20an%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20sergeant%20on%20Sunday%20recounted%20that%20despite%20announcements%20and%20efforts%20to%20convince%20people%20to%20avoid%20gathering%20in%20large%20numbers%2C%20the%20crowd%20remained%20unmanageable.%20He%20said%20the%20administration%20attempted%20to%20control%20the%20crowd%2C%20but%20people%20didn't%20listen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwe-kept-hoping-she-would-be-alive-witness-accounts-from-stampede-horror-7721252%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWe%20Kept%20Hoping%20She%20Would%20Be%20Alive%26quot%3B%3A%20Witness%20Accounts%20From%20Stampede%20Horror%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20Ajit%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20tri-service%20office%20at%20the%20railway%20station.%20While%20returning%20after%20my%20duty%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20huge%20crowd.%20I%20tried%20to%20convince%20people%20and%20also%20made%20announcements%2C%20appealing%20to%20people%20to%20avoid%20gathering%20on%20the%20platform%20in%20large%20numbers.%20The%20administration%20was%20working%20hard%20to%20prevent%20any%20mishap%2C%20but%20no%20one%20was%20listening.%20I%20also%20helped%20some%20injured%20people%20along%20with%20one%20of%20my%20friends.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20eyewitness%20said%20the%20crowd%20was%20beyond%