0of%20around%201%2C500%20general%20tickets%20exacerbated%20the%20situation%20and%20contributed%20to%20the%20overwhelming%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-maha-kumbh-rush-train-delays-led-to-new-delhi-railway-station-stampede-prayagraj-express-7721219%5C%22%3EWhat%20Led%20To%20Stampede%20At%20New%20Delhi%20Railway%20Station%20And%20How%20It%20Unfolded%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20affected%20passengers%2C%20Pappu%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Bihar's%20Patna%2C%20shared%20his%20grief%3A%20%26quot%3BMy%20mother%20died%20in%20the%20stampede.%20We%20were%20on%20our%20way%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDRF%20Commandant%20Daulat%20Ram%20Chaudhary%20confirmed%20that%20the%20situation%20was%20now%20under%20control.%20%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20is%20under%20control%20now.%20The%20injured%20have%20been%20evacuated.%20We%20received%20information%20about%20a%20stampede%20at%20platform%20no.%2014%20at%20the%20station.%20We%20are%20carrying%20out%20the%20rescue%20operations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDCP%20Railway%20KPS%20Malhotra%20said%20that%20while%20the%20authorities%20had%20anticipated%20a%20large%20crowd%2C%20the%20incident%20unfolded%20within%20moments.%20%26quot%3BWe%20expected%20the%20crowd%2C%20but%20it%20all%20happened%20in%20a%20fraction%20of%20time%2C%20and%20hence%20this%20situation%20occurred.%20The%20fact-finding%20will%20be%20done%20by%20the%20Railways.%20After%20inquiry%2C%20we%20will%20get%20to%20know%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20incident%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Railway%20Board%2C%20on%20Sunday%2C%20informed%20that%20a%20two-member%20high-level%20committee%20had%20been%20formed%20to%20investigate%20the%20matter%20and%20determine%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20stampede%20at%20New%20Delhi%20railway%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20two-member%20high-level%20committee%20has%20been%20