2https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2025%2F02%2F14%2Fus-news%2Fmeghan-markle-and-prince-harry-paying-big-bucks-to-dem-operatives%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublic%20records%20show%20that%20the%20Duke%20and%20Duchess%20of%20Sussex%20have%20invested%20heavily%20in%20top%20Democratic%20Party-aligned%20sources%2C%20including%20hiring%20a%20%26quot%3Bdisinformation%20expert%26quot%3B%20who%20has%20worked%20for%20a%20company%20involved%20in%20every%20major%20U.S.%20election%20since%20the%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20could%20further%20strain%20Prince%20Harry's%20relationship%20with%20his%20family%2C%20especially%20after%20his%20brother%2C%20Prince%20William%2C%20recently%20met%20with%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump.%20British%20media%20also%20reported%20that%20King%20Charles%20had%20maintained%20a%20good%20relationship%20with%20Trump%20since%20his%20presidency%2C%20and%20Trump%20himself%20had%20publicly%20expressed%20support%20for%20both%20royals%2C%20the%20report%20further%20stated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Archewell%20Foundation%2C%20the%20California-based%20nonprofit%20founded%20by%20Harry%20and%20Meghan%20in%202020%2C%20allocated%20%24146%2C500%20in%202023%20to%20Jiore%20Craig%2C%20an%20independent%20media%20strategist%20described%20as%20the%20Democrats'%20%26quot%3Bgo-to%26quot%3B%20expert%20on%20countering%20disinformation%2C%20according%20to%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublic%20records%20also%20show%20that%20Archewell%20donated%20%2425%2C000%20to%20the%20Marcy%20Lab%20School%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20where%20Craig%20joined%20the%20board%20in%202024.%20Additionally%2C%20federal%20filings%20reveal%20that%20Craig%20received%20%24120%2C000%20from%20the%20foundation%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECraig%2C%2033%2C%20previously%20worked%20at%20Washington%2C%20D.C.-based%20research%20firm%20Greenberg%2C%20Quinlan%2C%20and%20Rosner.%20A%20recognized%20election%20strategist%2C%20she%20rose%20to%20Senior%20Director%20of%20Digital%20Strategy%20in%202016%20and%20later%20served%20as%20Vice%20President%20from%202018%20to%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20firm's%20website%20highlights%20its%20role%20in%20Bill%20Clinton's%201992%20presidential%20victory%20and%20its%20ongoing%20efforts%20to%20help%20clients%20%26quot%3Bcampaign%2C%20win%2C%20govern%2C%20and%20win%20again.%26quot%3B%20Reports%20indicate%20that%20during%20the%20last%20election%20cycle%2C%20the%20firm%20worked%20to%20counter-narratives%20about%20Joe%20Biden's%20age%20and%20negative%20commentary%20about%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECraig%20describes%20her%20expertise%20on%20her%20LinkedIn%20profile%2C%20stating%20she%20%26quot%3Bdesigned%20and%20deployed%20Smart%20Social%20Listening%20strategies%20for%20political%20candidates%2C%20public%20officials%2C%20community%20leaders%2C%20and%20corporate%20leaders%20to%20stay%20on%20offence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArchewell%20also%20contributed%20%2490%2C000%20to%20Markup%20News%20Inc.%2C%20a%20New%20York-based%20nonprofit%20supported%20by%20Craigslist%20founder%20Craig%20Newmark%20and%20billionaire%20Democratic%20donor%20George%20Soros'%20Open%20Society%20Foundations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation's%20financial%20support%20for%20progressive%20Democratic%20causes%20has%20sparked%20criticism.%20Nile%20Gardiner%2C%20a%20fellow%20at%20the%20conservative%20Heritage%20Foundation%2C%20has%20called%20for%20congressional%20scrutiny%20of%20Archewell's%20donations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHarry%20and%20Meghan%20still%20retain%20royal%20titles%20and%20should%20not%20be%20engaging%20in%20any%20way%20in%20political%20activity%2C%26quot%3B%20Gardiner%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20outrageous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArchewell's%20largest%20donation%2C%20%24%20250%2C000%2C%20went%20to%20the%20Women's%20Wellness%20Space%2C%20a%20Pennsylvania-based%20charity%20founded%20in%202023%20by%20Ashley%20Biden%2C%20daughter%20of%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%20The%20organization%2C%20which%20opened%20in%202024%2C%20focuses%20on%20helping%20women%20affected%20by%20trauma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20also%20paid%20%24155%2C050%20to%20Herlihy%20Loughran%2C%20a%20firm%20run%20by%20former%20Buckingham%20Palace%20aides%20Beth%20Herlihy%20and%20Clara%20Loughran%2C%20for%20%26quot%3Bprogrammatic%20strategic%20services.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Duke%20and%20Duchess%20of%20Sussex%20told%20The%20New%20York%20Post%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20to%20note%20The%20Duke%20and%20Duchess%20did%20not%20endorse%20any%20candidate%20in%20the%20%5B2024%20presidential%5D%20election%20and%20to%20suggest%20they're%20trying%20to%20curry%20favour%20with%20the%20Democratic%20Party%20simply%20because%20a%20donation%20went%20to%20Ashley%20Biden's%20nonpartisan%20nonprofit%20focused%20on%20women's%20mental%20health%2C%20or%20because%20they%20hired%20a%20consultant%20specializing%20in%20digital%20safety-is%20misguided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Duke%20and%20Duchess%20are%20committed%20to%20investing%20in%20people%20and%20initiatives%20that%20truly%20make%20a%20difference.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeculation%20about%20Meghan's%20political%20ambitions%20has%20persisted%2C%20particularly%20after%20she%20and%20Harry%20travelled%20to%20New%20York%20in%202021%20to%20meet%20with%20prominent%20Democrats%2C%20including%20Governor%20Kathy%20Hochul%20and%20then-Mayor%20Bill%20de%20Blasio.%20That%20same%20year%2C%20reports%20revealed%20they%20also%20had%20a%20private%20video%20call%20with%20California%20Governor%20Gavin%20Newsom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Trump%20has%20been%20openly%20critical%20of%20Prince%20Harry%20and%20Meghan%20Markle.%20When%20asked%20about%20allegations%20that%20Harry%20may%20have%20misrepresented%20information%20on%20his%20U.S.%20visa%20application%2C%20Trump%20dismissed%20the%20issue%2C%20saying%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20leave%20him%20alone.%20He's%20got%20enough%2