h%20the%20ultrawealthy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Arizona%20lawmaker%20said%20personal%20wealth%20is%20aspirational%20for%20many%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20that%20are%20working%20class%2C%20poor%2C%20don't%20necessarily%20look%20at%20the%20ultrarich%20as%20their%20competitors%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20want%20to%20be%20rich%20someday.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20those%20voters%20would%20give%20Trump%2C%20Musk%2C%20and%20their%20allies%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20doubt%20until%20they%20were%20personally%20impacted%20by%20governmental%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGallego%20also%20predicted%20that%20Trump%20would%20face%20political%20backlash%20over%20the%20GOP's%20long-sought%20tax%20bill%2C%20which%20could%20include%20%244.5%20trillion%20in%20tax%20cuts%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmedicaid-trump-republicans-house-budget-social-security-medicare-musk-doge-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epotential%20spending%20reductions%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20programs%20like%20Medicaid%20and%20the%20Supplemental%20Nutrition%20Assistance%20Program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20when%20you're%20going%20to%20see%20people%20saying%2C%20'No%2C%20no%2C%20no%2C%20that's%20not%20what%20I%20want%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGallego%20has%20only%20been%20in%20the%20Senate%20for%20a%20few%20weeks%2C%20but%20he's%20no%20stranger%20to%20Washington.%20He%20served%20in%20the%20House%20for%20a%20decade%2C%20representing%20a%20Democratic-heavy%20district%20anchored%20in%20Phoenix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Gallego%20jumped%20into%20his%20state's%20Senate%20race%2C%20it%20was%20unclear%20whether%20then-Independent%20Sen.%20Kyrsten%20Sinema%20would%20also%20run.%20This%20had%20the%20potential%20to%20create%20a%20three-way%20race%2C%20which%20could%20have%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20the%20GOP%20to%20win%20the%20seat.%20However%2C%20Sinema%20eventually%20declined%20a%20reelection%20bid%2C%20and%20Galleg