%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGerman%20drone%20maker%20Quantum%20Systems%20says%20it%20will%20double%20its%20production%20capacity%20in%20Ukraine%20in%202025.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20has%20supplied%20Ukraine%20with%20drones%20since%20Russia%20launched%20its%20full-scale%20invasion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBillionaire%20Peter%20Thiel%20is%20one%20of%20the%20investors%20backing%20the%20startup.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGerman%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flithuanian-defense-company-drone-maker-rsi-europe-fpv-ukraine-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrone%3C%2Fa%3E%20manufacturer%20Quantum%20Systems%20has%20said%20it%20will%20double%20its%20production%20capacity%20in%20Ukraine%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20release%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20Peter%20Thiel-backed%20startup%20said%20the%20planned%20expansion%20reflected%20its%20%26quot%3Bunwavering%20commitment%26quot%3B%20to%20ensure%20Kyiv%20gets%20the%20technology%20it%20needs%20amid%20its%20ongoing%20war%20with%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuantum%2C%20which%20has%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMinstrategprom%2Fposts%2Fpfbid0cJKzmreZxTXyHeAsnCwdsod1sUHEK9qQpaDR3CsM8nRZ6Vxe6ku45RFynWP6Dhazl%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eestablished%3C%2Fa%3E%20two%20facilities%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20produces%20several%20uncrewed%20aerial%20systems%20used%20by%20Kyiv%2C%20including%20the%20%26quot%3BVector%26quot%3B%20reconnaissance%20drone%20and%20the%20%26quot%3BTrinity%26quot%3B%20mapping%20drone.%20Since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20invasion%2C%20Ukraine%20has%20ordered%20hundreds%20of%20these%20systems%20from%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuantum's%20Vector%20drone%20is%20primarily%20used%20for%20target%20identification%20and%20surveillance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20fly%20for%20up%20to%20180%20minutes%2C%20allows%20for%20real-time%20video%20streaming%20over%20a%20range%20of%2035%20kilometers%20(almost%2022%20miles)%2C%20and%20has%20vertical%20take-off%20and%20landing%20capability%2C%20the%20company%20says.%20The%20%26quot%3Brucksack%20portable%26quot%3B%20drone%20weighs%20just%2018%20pounds%20and%20is%20equipped%20with%20on-board%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Munich-based%20company%20also%20produces%20the%20%26quot%3BTrinity%20Pro%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BTrinity%20Tactical%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20are%20used%20for%20mapping%20and%20surveying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20drones%20can%20cover%20an%20area%20of%20700%20hectares%20in%20one%20flight%20and%20can%20fly%20for%2090%20minutes%2C%20Quantum%20says.%20They%20can%20use%20a%20variety%20of%20sensors%20to%20gather%20data%2C%20such%20as%20multi-spectral%20cameras%20and%20LiDAR%20scanners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20can%20be%20deployed%20to%20help%20with%20environmental%20and%20battle%20damage%20assessments%2C%20as%20well%20as%20surveying%20and%20mapping%20key%20infrastructure%20and%20terrain%2C%20among%20other%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202015%2C%20Quantum%20has%20raised%20more%20than%20%24200%20million%2C%20per%20Crunchbase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeter-thiel%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBillionaire%20and%20PayPal%20cofounder%20Peter%20Thiel%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20of%20the%20investors%20to%20have%20pumped%20money%20into%20the%20company%2C%20taking%20part%20in%20a%20financing%20round%20alongside%20Project%20A%20and%20Sanno%20Capital%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20time%2C%20Thiel%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20future%20of%20UAS%20is%20in%20neither%20software%20nor%20hardware%20alone%2C%20but%20in%20the%20intelligent%20synthesis%20of%20the%20two.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20that%20understanding%2C%20Quantum-Systems%20is%20a%20leap%20ahead%20of%20its%20competition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrone-maker-supplies-ukraine-tesla-approach-innovation-peter-t