%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20had%20also%20announced%20that%20India%20and%20the%20US%20will%20work%20together%20like%20%26quot%3Bnever%20before%26quot%3B%20to%20confront%20the%20threat%20of%20%26quot%3Bradical%20Islamic%20terror%26quot%3B%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20that%20Rana%20has%20filed%20a%20final%20appeal%20on%20humanitarian%20grounds%20in%20a%20US%20appeals%20forum%20and%20this%20could%20delay%20the%20extradition%20by%20a%20few%20weeks.%20Experts%20said%20that%20this%20is%20a%20legal%20matter%20and%20will%20not%20affect%20the%20strong%20diplomatic%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20the%20US.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERana's%20Role%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistani-American%20David%20Coleman%20Headley%2C%20one%20of%20the%20main%20conspirators%20of%20the%2026%2F11%20attacks%2C%20had%20testified%20against%20Rana.%20Headley%20had%20revealed%20during%20his%20interrogation%20in%20the%20United%20States%20that%20he%20had%20travelled%20to%20India%20five%20times%20between%202007%20and%202008%20and%20conducted%20a%20recce%20of%20possible%20targets%20in%20Mumbai%20for%20the%20attacks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeadley%20had%20said%20he%20had%20visited%20India%20using%20a%20five-year%20visa%20that%20Rana%20had%20helped%20him%20obtain%20and%20that%20his%20co-conspirator%20had%20also%20aided%20him%20in%20opening%20an%20immigration%20company%20to%20hide%20his%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20Rana%20was%20acquitted%20by%20a%20US%20court%20on%20charges%20of%20abetting%20the%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%20but%20was%20convicted%20of%20providing%20material%20support%20to%20the%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20and%20helping%20a%20terror%20plot%20in%20Denmark.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739645160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fpg8pkbj_tahawwur-rana_625x300_25_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F26-11-mumbai-at