e%20BBC%20they%20are%20hiding%20in%20their%20homes%20as%20the%20rebels%20advance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A69%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1m5dppk5xmo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1m5dppk5xmo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1m5dppk5xmo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20worked%20in%20a%20children's%20secondhand%20store.%20Here's%20what%20you%20should%20know%20before%20donating.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Adorable%205-Year-Old%20Shopping%3A%20Trying%20on%20a%20Hoodie%20in%20a%20Thrift%20Store%20Sale%20-%20stock%20photo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ab906f6630eb10385c4030%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20(not%20pictured)%20says%20that%20only%2020%25%20of%20the%20donated%20clothes%20were%20resold.%3Cp%3ENatalia%20Lebedinskaia%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20worked%20for%20a%20year%20at%20a%20secondhand%20store%20selling%20used%20clothing%20and%20toys.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20had%20to%20reject%20many%20donated%20items%20based%20on%20their%20condition.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20want%20people%20to%20be%20more%20mindful%20of%20what%20they%20donate%20instead.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20worked%20at%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fwhere-to-sell-clothes-shoes-bags-online-2019-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econsignment%20store%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20my%20final%20year%20of%20high%20school.%20Each%20shift%2C%20customers%20would%20bring%20bags%20of%20old%20clothing%20for%20us%20to%20sort%20through%20to%20determine%20if%20it%20was%20acceptable%20to%20sell.%20Being%20a%20consignment%20store%2C%20customers%20would%20get%20a%20percentage%20of%20the%20profits%20if%20their%20items%20were%20sold.%20If%20the%20items%20were%20unacceptable%2C%20we%20would%20put%20them%20aside%20in%20a%20bag%20to%20donate%20to%20local%20charities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20working%20there%2C%20I%20must've%20sorted%20through%20hundreds%20of%20pieces%20of%20clothing%2C%20many%20of%20which%20we%20couldn't%20sell.%20This%20should%20not%20be%20surprising%2C%20given%20that%20only%20about%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nist.gov%2Fnews-events%2Fnews%2F2022%2F05%2Fyour-clothes-can-have-afterlife%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E15%25%20of%20clothes%20donated%20to%20secondhand%20stores%20are%20resold%20or%20reused%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20items%20I%20rejected%20had%20obvious%20imperfections%3A%20visible%20stains%2C%20holes%2C%20or%20tears%2C%20making%20it%20extremely%20unlikely%20anyone%20else%20would%20want%20to%20wear%20them.%20We%20would%20even%20receive%20items%20our%20store%20didn't%20sell%2C%20such%20as%20used%20underwear.%20It%20was%20frustrating%20to%20constantly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-thrift-shop-in-every-state-yelp-2017-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereceive%20donations%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20so%20evidently%20unfit%20to%20sell%2C%20making%20me%20feel%20as%20if%20people%20were%20just%20using%20our%20store%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20clothing%20they%20no%20longer%20wanted%20without%20thinking%20about%20where%20it%20would%20end%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cd88d286-e0c3-44b9-91d2-d84e6c8ac316%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20had%20to%20ship%20rejected%20clothes%20to%20charities%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20clothing%20we%20rejected%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-rated-charities-social-causes-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edonated%20to%20local%20charities%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20we%20didn't%20track%20what%20happened%20to%20it%20after%20it%20left%20the%20store.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20likely%20that%20the%20clothing%20will%20get%20thrown%20out%20somewhere%20down%20the%20line%2C%20becoming%20part%20of%20the%20EPA%20estimate%20in%202018%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epa.gov%2Ffacts-and-figures-about-materials-waste-and-recycling%2Ftextiles-material-specific-data%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E11.3%20million%20tons%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20textiles%20were%20sent%20to%20landfills%2C%20comprising%207.7%25%20of%20all%20landfilled%20waste.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20there's%20been%20increasing%20awareness%20of%20the%20harms%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-quit-fast-fashion-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efast-fashion%20industry%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20the%20mass%20production%20of%20cheap%2C%20low-quality%20clothing%2C%20leading%20people%20to%20look%20to%20secondhand%20clothing%20stores%20as%20a%20more%20sustainable%20alternative.%20It%20can%20be%20especially%20appealing%20to%20parents%20of%20young%20children%20who%20are%20constantly%20outgrowing%20their%20clothes.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20this%20to%20say%2C%20I%20want%20people%20to%20be%20more%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-fast-fashion-shein-temu-trouble-second-trump-term-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emindful%20of%20what%20they%20do%20with%20their%20old%20clothing%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20take%20a%20good%20look%20at%20the%20items%20they're%20giving%20away%20to%20ask%20themselves%2C%20honestly%2C%20if%20anyone%20else%20would%20want%20to%20use%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2204df0ef8-bd1a-4863-9d2a-6f2e5e350ef9%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20other%20alternatives%20for%20kids'%20stuff%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20also%20important%20to%20consider%20other%20alternatives%20before%20donating%20clothing%20to%20secondhand%20stores.%20Do%20you%20have%20friends%20with%20younger%20children%3F%20Maybe%20they%20would%20appreciate%20your%20child's%20old%20clothes%20(if%20it's%20not%20in%20good%20enough%20condition%20for%20your%20friends%2C%20secondhand%20stores%20probably%20don't%20want%20it%20either).%20I%20personally%20try%20to%20mend%20or%20upcycle%20my%20clothes%20to%20extend%20their%20life%20as%20much%20as%20possible.%20If%20clothing%20is%20in%20really%20bad%20shape%2C%20you%20can%20look%20into%20textile%20recycling%20programs%20in%20your%20area%20or%20repurpose%20them%20as%20household%20items%20such%20as%20cleaning%20rags.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAddressing%20this%20as%20individuals%20starts%20with%20being%20intentional%20about%20what%20we%20buy.%20Before%20buying%20clothes%2C%20reflect%20on%20whether%20you%20or%20your%20child%20%3Cem%3Ereally%3C%2Fem%3E%20needs%20them%20and%20where%20they%20might%20end%20up%20once%20you%20finish%20them.%20Talk%20to%20family%20and%20friends%20about%20appropriate%20gifts%20for%20your%20child%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%2C%20non-material%20gifts%2C%20such%20as%20experiences%2C%20can%20be%20more%20meaningful.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20changes%20may%20seem%20small%2C%20but%20they%20could%20make%20a%20difference%20in%20how%20we%20treat%20our%20old%20clothes%20in%20the%20long%20term.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-parents-should-know-before-donating-kids-clothes-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739641922000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2