bachchans-visit-to-a-bangkok-strip-club-he-kept-saying-mind-blowing%2Farticleshow%2F118281487.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEngland%20Cricket%20Is%20Naive...%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex-Star%20After%203-0%20Loss%20To%20India%20Ahead%20Of%20CT%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20England%20cricketer%20Mark%20Butcher%20has%20raised%20concerns%20about%20whether%20England%20possess%20enough%20experience%20in%20the%2050-over%20format%20to%20compete%20effectively%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Champions%20Trophy.%20His%20remarks%20came%20after%20England%20suffered%20a%20humiliating%203-0%20series%20defeat%20against%20India%2C%20exposing%20significant%20weaknesses%20in%20their%20ODI%20setup.%20Speaking%20on%20the%20Wisden%20Cricket%20Weekly%20podcast%20during%20England's%20third%20ODI%20loss%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Butcher%20highlighted%20the%20lack%20of%20match%20experience%20among%20the%20squad.%20England%20fielded%20several%20inexperienced%20players%20in%20the%20series%2C%20including%20Jacob%20Bethell%2C%20who%20had%20played%20just%2016%20List%20A%20games%20before%20making%20his%20ODI%20debut%20last%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGus%20Atkinson%2C%20who%20made%20his%20international%20debut%20in%202023%20after%20featuring%20in%20only%20two%20List%20A%20matches%2C%20endured%20a%20difficult%20tour%2C%20conceding%20139%20runs%20across%20two%20ODIs.%20Following%20Bethell's%20injury%2C%20England%20recalled%20Tom%20Banton%2C%20who%20hadn't%20played%20a%20single%2050-over%20match%20since%20his%20last%20ODI%20appearance%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20thing%20that%20sprung%20to%20my%20mind%20during%20the%20first%20two%20ODIs%20was%20just%20how%20naive%20most%20of%20our%20cricket%20is%20in%20the%2050-over%20format%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Butcher%2C%20as%20quoted%20from%20Wisden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20'why%20might%20that%20be%3F'.%20It's%20because%20we%20don't%20play%20any.%20There%20is%20a%20world%20of%20difference%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20tempo%20that%20the%20game%20needs%20to%20continuously%20be%20played%20at.%20I%20don't%20mean%20that%20the%20tempo%20is%20a%20rigid%20graph%20that%20only%20goes%20up%2C%20the%20tempo%20needs%20to%20fluctuate%20in%2050-over%20cricket%20in%20a%20way%20that%20it%20doesn't%20need%20to%20in%2020-over%20cricket.%20Having%20that%20skill%20and%20nous%20and%20game%20awareness%20to%20know%20when%20to%20put%20the%20foot%20down%20and%20when%20to%20ease%20off%20a%20little%20but%2C%20when%20to%20sit%20in%20and%20when%20to%20go%20hard%2C%20is%20something%20that%20only%20comes%20with%20playing%20lots%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20remember%20back%20in%20the%2090s%20when%20England%20would%20play%20three%20Texaco%20Trophy%20matches%20during%20the%20course%20of%20the%20summer%2C%20the%20sum%20total%20of%20England's%2050-over%20cricket%20would%20be%20three%20to%20six%20matches%20per%20summer.%20They'd%20be%20playing%20against%20Indian%20sides%2C%20or%20West%20Indian%20sides%20or%20Australian%20sides%2C%20the%20difference%20in%20number%20of%20caps%20between%20them%20and%20our%20players%20was%20three%20times%20more%20on%20the%20other%20team.%20We're%20kind%20of%20back%20in%20that%20situation%20now%20whereby%20the%20India%20players%20will%20out%20number%20the%20number%20of%20caps%20of%20even%20someone%20like%20Jos%20Buttler%20for%20example%2C%20by%20at%20least%20two%20to%20one%20or%20three%20to%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20our%20guys%20will%20be%20a%20lot%20better%20for%20the%20run.%20Gus%20Atkinson%20has%20had%20a%20pretty%20chastening%20trip%20and%20that's%20not%20a%20bad%20thing.%20He's%20basically%20found%20the%20game%20far%20too%20easy%20up%20to%20this%20point%20and%20has%20run%20into%20the%20first%20road%20block.%20Being%20a%20very%20talented%20boy%20and%20somebody%20who%20has%20the%20hunger%20and%20desire%20to%20be%20the%20very%20best%2C%20he%20will%20be%20better%20for%20the%20experience%20of%20a%20flogging%20in%20India.%20But%20if%20you're%20talking%20about%20winning%20a%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20time%2C%20it's%20not%20likely%20is%20it%3F%20That%20our%20team%20and%20the%20make-up%20of%20it%20and%20the%20experience%20of%20it%20is%20going%20to%20have%20the%20skill%20and%20the%20nous%20and%20the%20know-how%20to%20win%20what%20is%20a%20very%20difficult%20form%20of%20cricket%2C%2050-over%20cricket.%20It%20requires%20more%20than%20just%20putting%20your%20foot%20to%20the%20floor%20and%20keeping%20it%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20stark%20contrast%2C%20India's%20young%20players%20have%20considerably%20more%20experience%20in%20the%20format.%20Shubman%20Gill%2C%20at%20just%2025%2C%20has%20already%20played%2050%20ODIs%20and%20over%20100%20List%20A%20matches.%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20who%20made%20his%20ODI%20debut%20in%20the%20second%20match%20of%20the%20series%20in%20Cuttack%2C%20has%20already%20featured%20in%2030%20List%20A%20games%20despite%20being%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20his%20professional%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEngland's%20campaign%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20will%20begin%20on%20February%2022%20in%20Lahore%2C%20where%20they%20will%20take%20on%20arch-rivals%20Australia.%20They%20will%20also%20face%20Afghanistan%20and%20South%20Africa%20in%20the%20group%20stage%2C%20hoping%20to%20overcome%20their%20recent%20struggles%20and%20make%20a%20strong%20impact%20in%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739635440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fd3nrvfd8_team-england-bcci_625x300_10_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fengland-cricket-is-naive-ex-star-a