air%20travel%20to%20Europe%20and%20caused%20more%20problems%20for%20the%20already%20struggling%20country%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20also%20drew%20international%20awareness%20to%20Iceland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETravelers%20from%20around%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20drawn%20in%20by%20the%20weak%20krona%20and%20creative%20marketing%20by%20budget%20airlines%20promoting%20Iceland%20as%20a%20desirable%20stopover%20between%20Europe%20and%20the%20Americas%20%E2%80%94%20started%20rolling%20in.%20Iceland's%20annual%20visitor%20numbers%20grew%20by%20328%25%20between%202010%20and%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTourism%20was%20extremely%20important%20to%20get%20us%20back%20on%20our%20feet%20after%20the%20crash%2C%20and%20it%20grew%20into%20our%20biggest%20export%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20Sigr%C3%AD%C3%B0ur%20D%C3%B6gg%20Gu%C3%B0mundsd%C3%B3ttir%2C%20then%20the%20head%20of%20Visit%20Iceland%2C%20told%20ADP%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20Japan%20is%20facing%20economic%20challenges%20of%20its%20own%2C%20including%20a%20weak%20currency%2C%20high%20inflation%2C%20and%20shrinking%20GDP.%20Japan%20is%20also%20dealing%20with%20an%20aging%20population%2C%20low%20birth%20rate%2C%20and%20a%20labor%20shortage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTourism's%20a%20quick%20win%20for%20many%20of%20these%20places%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alan%20Fyall%2C%20the%20Visit%20Orlando%20endowed%20chair%20of%20tourism%20marketing%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Central%20Florida's%20Rosen%20College%20of%20Hospitality%20Management%20who%20studies%20sustainable%20tourism%2C%20said%20of%20countries%20with%20struggling%20economies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTourism%20can%20be%20a%20very%2C%20very%20powerful%20economic%20and%20social%20force%20for%20good.%20There's%20no%20question.%20However%2C%20it's%20like%20everything%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20how%20you%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22713bcaed-d022-4d2a-b5f3-c7d47e90b26e%5C%22%3EWhen%20overtourism%20becomes%20a%20problem%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20travel%20industry%20news%20site%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fskift.com%2F2019%2F09%2F11%2Fthe-rise-and-fall-of-icelands-tourism-miracle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESkift%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20put%20it%20in%202019%2C%20Iceland%20became%20%26quot%3Bthe%20poster%20child%20for%20the%20positive%20and%20negative%20effects%20of%20the%20overtourism%20phenomenon%26quot%3B%20as%20tourism%20evolved%20into%20the%20country's%20biggest%20industry%20in%20a%20relatively%20short%20number%20of%20years.%20The%20impacts%20of%20the%20tourism%20boom%20included%20crowding%20at%20hot%20spots%2C%20disrespectful%20tourist%20behavior%2C%20stress%20on%20infrastructure%20and%20natural%20areas%2C%20and%20higher%20prices%20for%20locals%20and%20visitors%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20potential%20over-reliance%20on%20tourism%20as%20an%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225763%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Crowd%20on%20busy%20Tokyo%20street.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ad40a67bb3f854015cbc28%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223842%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmeyoko%20market%2C%20a%20popular%20tourist%20area%20in%20central%20Tokyo.%3Cp%3ERichard%20A.%20Brooks%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJapan%20is%20much%20larger%20than%20Iceland%20%E2%80%94%20in%20size%2C%20population%2C%20and%20GDP%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20country%20is%20already%20facing%20some%20of%20the%20same%20overtourism%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMasaru%20Takayama%2C%20chairperson%20at%20the%20Japan%20Alliance%20of%20Responsible%20Travel%20Agencies%20and%20an%20expert%20in%20sustainable%20travel%2C%20said%20Kyoto%2C%20where%20he%20is%20based%2C%20has%20become%20%26quot%3Ba%20capital%20of%20overtourism.%26quot%3B%20The%20central%20part%20of%20the%20city%20has%20been%20inundated%20with%20tourists%20who%20are%20consuming%20public%20resources%20and%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20local%20residents%20to%20go%20about%20their%20daily%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20elders%20here%20who%20can%20ride%20buses%20and%20subway%20for%20free%2C%20but%20there's%20no%20seats%20available%20for%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETakayama%20said%20local%20businesses%20have%20also%20changed%20to%20accommodate%20the%20tourists.%20He%20said%20his%20favorite%20restaurants%20are%20within%20walking%20distance%20but%20that%20it's%20difficult%20to%20actually%20go%20because%20tourists%20make%20reservations%20months%20in%20advance.%20The%20restaurants%20have%20also%20raised%20prices%20and%20switched%20up%20their%20menus%20to%20cater%20more%20to%20foreigners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20literally%20see%20these%20places%2C%20but%20you%20cannot%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20are%20really%20losing%20the%20authenticity%20of%20what%20it%20was%2C%20what%20was%20nice%20about%20Kyoto.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20rise%20in%20rental%20properties%20has%20also%20led%20to%20higher%20prices%20and%20taxes%20for%20locals%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20don't%20work%20in%20tourism-related%20industries%20and%20therefore%20are%20experiencing%20the%20downsides%20of%20tourism%20without%20much%20of%20the%20benefits%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJapan%20has%20already%20taken%20some%20measures%20to%20address%20issues%20with%20tourism.%20Last%20year%20officials%20in%20Kyoto%20banned%20tourists%20from%20certain%20alleyways%20in%20Gion%2C%20the%20popular%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftourist-banned-japan-kyoto-gion-geisha-rules-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Egeisha%20district%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20after%20complaints%20from%20locals%20about%20visitors'%20behavior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFujikawaguchiko%2C%20a%20small%20town%20near%20Mount%20Fuji%2C%20said%20last%20year%20it%20was%20building%20a%20mesh%20barrier%20to%20block%20a%20popular%20photo%20spot%20for%20tourists%20after%20residents%20complained%20about%20disrespectful%20behavior.%20Japan%20also%20announced%20last%20year%20new%20regulations%20and%20a%20tourist%20tax%20for%20climbing%20Mount%20Fuji%2C%20a%20UNESCO%20World%20Heritage%20site%2C%20due%20to%20overcrowding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20experts%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI%20said%20Japan%20should%20focus%20on%20a%20proactive%20approach%20to%20managing%20tourism%20that%20prioritizes%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20locals%20alongside%20the%20benefits%20of%20tourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22649e30d6-123b-4733-be4a-1b99dcb56e66%5C%22%3EProactive%20measures%20against%20overtourism%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFyall%20said%20Japan%20is%20relatively%20new%20to%20the%20tourism%20game%2C%20only%20emerging%20as%20a%20common%20destination%20for%20travelers%20in%20the%20past%2010%20to%2015%20years.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHe%20also%20said%20the%20country%20has%20been%20relatively%20cautious%20about%20promoting%20tourism%20and%20not%20quite%20as%20aggressive%20as%20other%20destinations.%20But%20now%20that%20the%20yen%20is%20weak%2C%20he%20said%20it's%20%26quot%3Bbonanza%20time%26quot%3B%20for%20travelers%20from%20China%20and%20the%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tourists%20take%20selfies%20in%20front%20of%20Buddhist%20temple.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ad41337bb3f854015cbc33%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223335%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETourists%20take%20selfies%20with%20the%20Hozomon%20Gate%20at%20Senso-ji%20Temple%20in%20Asakusa%2C%20Tokyo.%3Cp%3EStanislav%20Kogiku%2FSOPA%20Images%2FLightRocket%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnna%20Abelson%2C%20an%20adjunct%20professor%20at%20New%20York%20University's%20Jonathan%20M.%20Tisch%20Center%20of%20Hospitality%2C%20said%20Iceland%20was%20not%20initially%20prepared%20for%20its%20tourism%20boom%2C%20but%20that%20the%20pandemic%2C%20while%20challenging%20for%20the%20tourism%20industry%2C%20allowed%20the%20country%20to%20shift%20its%20focus%20on%20fostering%20a%20sustainable%20travel%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIceland%20has%20adopted%20several%20measures%20to%20address%20overtourism%2C%20including%20a%20tourism%20tax%2C%20which%20is%20applied%20to%20hotel%20rooms%2C%20cruises%2C%20and%20campsites%20and%20is%20used%20to%20support%20sustainability%20efforts%20and%20mitigate%20the%20environmental%20impact%20of%20tourism.%20The%20country%20has%20also%20invested%20millions%20in%20improving%20infrastructure%20at%20popular%20tourist%20spots%2C%20building%20much-needed%20parking%20lots%2C%20restrooms%2C%20and%20designated%20trails%2C%20and%20encouraging%20visitors%20to%20travel%20to%20less-explored%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbelson%20said%20Japan%20should%20be%20proactive%20%E2%80%94%20rather%20than%20reactive%20%E2%80%94%20at%20addressing%20the%20problems%20with%20overtourism%20or%20risk%20getting%20to%20a%20point%20where%20locals%20take%20out%20their%20frustration%20on%20tourists.%20In%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-of-protesters-rallying-against-overtourism-in-barcelona-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBarcelona%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20summer%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20protesters%20sprayed%20visitors%20dining%20at%20restaurants%20in%20the%20city%20center%20with%20water%20guns%20during%20a%20demonstration%20against%20overtourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbelson%20said%20one%20thing%20Japan%20could%20do%20is%20appeal%20to%20tourists%20directly%20to%20encourage%20better%20behavior%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpalaupledge.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EPalau%20Pledge%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20which%20visitors%20to%20the%20island%20nation%20are%20required%20to%20sign%20a%20pledge%20%26quot%3Bto%20act%20in%20an%20ecologically%20and%20culturally%20responsible%20way.%26quot%3B%20She%20said%20Japan%20could%20also%20focus%20on%20spreading%20tourists%20out%2C%20as%20Thailand%20has%20done%20by%20promoting%20lesser-known%20regions%20like%20Chang%20Mai%20and%20other%20islands%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20areas%20that%20are%20already%20experiencing%20overcrowding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETakayama%20said%20he%20thinks%20the%20Japanese%20government%20is%20still%20focusing%20on%20tourism%20quantity%20rather%20than%20quality%2C%20the%20latter%20of%20which%20he%20says%20is%20necessary%20for%20sustainable%20tourism.%20While%20there%20are%20sustainable%20tourism%20guidelines%20%E2%80%94%20set%20by%20the%20Global%20Sustainable%20Tourism%20Council%2C%20which%20Takayama%20is%20part%20of%20%E2%80%94%20he%20said%20implementation%20and%20action%20is%20another%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20agreed%20that%20Japan%20could%20encourage%20tourists%20to%20visit%20lesser-known%20places%2C%20but%20that%20the%20government%20would%20also%20have%20to%20ensure%20those%20destinations%20are%20prepared%20and%20could%20accommodate%20tourists%20in%20a%20sustainable%20way.%20He%20also%20said%20the%20government%20could%20do%20more%20to%20try%20and%20attract%20the%20right%20kinds%20of%20tourists%20who%20are%20interested%20in%20traveling%20responsibly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJapan%20is%20still%20a%20very%20good%20place%20to%20visit%2C%20and%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20sanctuaries%20that%20people%20are%20not%20aware%20of%2C%20which%20they%20should%20explore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20love%20to%20have%20you%20as%20long%20as%20you%20obey%20the%20local%20rules.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20news%20tip%20or%20a%20story%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Akvlamis%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ekvlamis%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20via%20the%20encrypted-messaging%20app%20Signal%20%40kelseyv.21.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2