20crypto%20investment.%20Over%20half%E2%80%94%2053%25%E2%80%94of%20respondents%20rank%20volatility%20as%20a%20top%20challenge%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20digital%20assets%2C%20leading%20some%20to%20discourage%20clients%20from%20putting%20money%20in%20the%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BClients%20trust%20us%20to%20secure%20their%20financial%20future.%20We%20can't%20be%20rolling%20the%20dice.%20If%20that's%20all%20we're%20going%20to%20do%2C%20then%20they%20don't%20need%20us.%20They%20can%20go%20to%20a%20casino%2C%26quot%3B%20Kashif%20A.%20Ahmed%2C%20a%20certified%20financial%20planner%20and%20the%20president%20of%20American%20Private%20Wealth%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20him%2C%20there's%20no%20way%20to%20justify%20adding%20crypto%20to%20a%20client's%20portfolio%20if%20its%20leading%20use%20is%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbitcoin-price-prediction-btc-crypto-meme-coins-market-forecast-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epure%20speculation%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20agreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20different%20roles%20that%20investments%20in%20a%20portfolio%20can%20play%3A%20It%20can%20be%20high%20risk-high%20return%20potential.%20It%20can%20be%20risk-mitigating.%20It%20can%20be%20protecting%20against%20inflation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Noah%20Damsky%2C%20a%20certified%20financial%20advisor%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20Marina%20Wealth%20Advisors.%20%26quot%3BCrypto%20doesn't%20really%20have%20any%20set%20purpose.%20I%20guess%20it%20could%20return%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20that's%20just%20speculation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e1d5372a-203d-46c9-b8cb-9d049f05a651%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EReputational%20risk%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBulls%20may%20be%20quick%20to%20point%20out%20that%20crypto%20speculation%20has%20been%20massively%20profitable%20lately.%20Bitcoin%20soared%20by%20about%20114%25%20in%202024%2C